			h5 Terms and conditions 
			p.terms Competition for Tictail online stores only. Winner will receive Sosinski Interactive Photography package for their online store including the spin plug-in for 1 full year with up to 50 product spins. Tictail will cover the costs of shipping the products to and from photo studio in Malmö, Sweden, up to a cost of €300. The photo shoot can be divided into two separate sessions if need be. The spins will go live by latest 10 business days after date of photo shoot. All items for the photo shoot must be shipped by latest 31st March, 2014. Items will be returned within 15 business days after date of photo shoot. Sosinski Interactive Photography plug-in will expire 1 year after it has gone live on the winner's Tictail store. License agreement and contract must be signed prior to installation of plug-in.  